@Triplehammer : 
The English site did not have czechmegaswingers001part3, czechmegaswingers002part3, or czechmegaswingers003part5 and I am too lazy to see if they are missing or they just split the video in to less parts.

It is my understanding that the Czech sites (swingersakce.cz & www.udelejse.cz) has been around awhile and has stockpiled up videos.  They have been subtitling them in English but not necessarily distributing them in the same order they were originally done in the Czech Republic. A new czech casting comes out about one a day, but there is no logical ordering (# or name) for which one is released next.  Other releases (mega swingers, parties, streets, and now amateurs) come out sporadically about once a week, but seem to at least be in order.

I will make another "update" pack later this month with czech mega swingers 11-13, czech streets 45+, the new "czech amateurs", and any new releases of czech casting and czech parties.  If I find that the English site does not have videos on the cezch site mentioned in the above comment, I might include them in the next update too.
